   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>( listening to the story)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Leon.. <BR>It's a long story....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>What happened? It isn't a good thing?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>About 10 years ago, in the North continent a<BR><FONT color=#a82424> shining star </FONT> emerged. This was the star that Sage predicted, even though everyone assume is a good omen, but it was not...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>I've never heard of those that you have mentioned.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Immediately after the stars appeared, from the northern continents monster start spreading across the land .<BR>Among them were monsters whom we've never came across before.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" image="QW_CataractGateway.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>According to investigators, these monsters are moving from North to South. Their goal is <FONT color=#a82424>Calderock Village</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>What family? Do the monster want them?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Later on, Master investigated further and realised that these monsters were pursuing a certain family.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>Why are they being pursued?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>It was a man named Leon, a woman named Clara, and their young daughter. In the beginning my Master suspect they had disturbed those monsters unwittingly, however it doesn't seem to be that way.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>He must have been a brave man.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Master may have noticed something yet didn't breathe a word about it. However when they arrive in town, they are in a mist of battling the stronghold. Leon took charge of the frontline fightning against the monsters.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-i" mid="64"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>At first, the villagers were complaining about him luring the monster here.<BR>Gradually, they have a change in attitude and took part in the combats.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-i" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" mid="66"><![CDATA[<html> This situation sounds like Forest of Death. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The monster were led by a cunning Red Dark Elf.<BR>They were too powerful and strong to fight against.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-j" image="QW_17.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-k" mid="68"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>We planned to lure those monsters into the Forest of Death and kill the whole lot once and for all in that area. In this way we can also reduce the  pollution made to the surrounding area.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-k" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-l" mid="70"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>During the process of luring monster many were sacrificed. This is a battle of casualities. Even though many heroes were sacrificed, the Monsters are gaining advantage of the war situation. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-l" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-m" mid="72"><![CDATA[<html>How did things go for him?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Leon helped his wife and daughter escape, leaving behind a few words and a pendant to my Master.<BR>And he headed through the woods of Forest Sanctuary, all alone.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-m" image="QW_15.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-n" mid="74"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything I can help?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>No one ever heard from him since then <BR>I retreated from the battle as my master commanded. But my master didn’t move. It seems like he is waiting for Leon. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-n" image="QW_15.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" mid="78"><![CDATA[<html> Yes, I'll start researching. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I'm sorry to bother you... But can you go to the Forest Sanctuary and check on Leon? I'm sure those information will give my Master a peace of mind.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="QW_15.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>There should be some clues lying around.<BR>Comb the Forest Sanctuary from top to bottom, and let me know what you managed to gather.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3-a" mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>(You explain what happened at the Forest Sanctuary.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Did you manage to find anything related to Leon?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
